<li id="note-2"><em>Covert Action in Chile, 1963‑1973, a Staff Report of The Select Committee to Study Governmental Operations with Respect to Intelligence Activities (US Senate) </em>December 18, 1975, p.39 <sup>↩</sup></li>
</ol>
