<p>&nbsp;<br />
During the Old Regime under the reign of Louis XVI, the aristocracy lost their heads under the guillotine. In the 21th Century, the masters of the universe, spread breadcrumbs by way of food stamps to a society relegated to systemic government poverty and dependency. The only cake consumed these days requires a hedge fund account to pay for the icing and toppings.</p>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">
<tbody>
<tr>
